  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators are measuring hepatocellular carcinoma(HCC)stiffness using Acoustic
      Radiation Force Impulse (ARFI) technique to enhance the diagnostic accuracy for HCC
      stratifications and treatment efficacy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Regression modelings as well as validity testings including cut-off identification will be
      acquired by performing both qualitative and quantitative measurements of HCC using reference
      diagnostic modalities e.g. pathology grading, dynamic CT scanning, etc.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
